leadership_approach|vision_results_people_process|concentrated|vision|results|people|process|Recognised for Vision-first leadership|This pattern shows up in how you set longer-range direction and connect effort to future possibility. Others experience a clearer sense of direction, purpose, and future possibility.|At its best, Vision gives people a clearer sense of direction, purpose, and future possibility. It narrows when Vision alone is not enough, so bring Results, People, or Process in earlier when the situation needs clearer outcomes, decisions, and next steps, deeper trust, communication, and shared confidence, or stronger structure, coordination, and repeatability.|active|leadership_approach::vision_results_people_process::concentrated
leadership_approach|vision_results_people_process|paired|vision|results|people|process|Recognised for Vision and Results working together|This pattern shows up in how you combine setting longer-range direction with deciding what needs to happen. Others experience a clearer sense of direction, purpose, and future possibility alongside clear priorities, practical movement, and a stronger sense of what happens next.|At its best, Vision and Results help leadership handle longer-range direction, future context, and wider meaning and clearer outcomes, decisions, and next steps. It narrows when the pair runs ahead of People or Process, so bring them in earlier when the situation needs deeper trust, communication, and shared confidence or stronger structure, coordination, and repeatability.|active|leadership_approach::vision_results_people_process::paired
